\u00e5 v\u00e6re offensive, men r\u00e5dmannen har ikke fulgt opp, sa H\u00f8yres Ingrid Skj\u00f8tskift da formannskapet behandlet saken tirsdag."]}, {"field": "category0", "value": "nyheter"}, {"field": "category1", "value": "nyheter|trondheim"}, {"field": "contenthash", "value": "00ef2e3aeff40cae2fb05076233be16d042850f373e347b76319ccee1ce96017"}, {"field": "createtime", "value": "2016-01-19T09:47:32.000Z"}, {"field": "description", "value": "Et flertall i formannskapet i Trondheim p\u00e5legger r\u00e5dmannen \u00e5 sette fart p\u00e5 innf\u00f8ringen av arbeidsplikt for unge sosialhjelpsmottakere i kommunen."}, {"field": "dominantimage", "value": "http://static.polarismedia.no/skins/prod/publication/adressa/gfx/applefavicon.png"}, {"field": "dominantimagedimensions", "value": "256x256"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnail", "value": "http://content-thumbnail.cxpublic.com/content/dominantthumbnail/601f9dedc08a7ec3c142a314c1d8cd6678470675.jpg?592820a3"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnaildimensions", "value": "256x256"}, {"field": "heading", "value": "P\u00e5legger r\u00e5dmannen \u00e5 innf\u00f8re aktivitetsplikt -adressa.no"}, {"field": "id", "value": "601f9dedc08a7ec3c142a314c1d8cd6678470675"}, {"field": "keyword", "value": ["Politikk", "ingrid skj\u00f8tskift"]}, {"field": "keywords", "value": "Politikk,ingrid skj\u00f8tskift"}, {"field": "kw-category", "value": ["nyheter", "trondheim"]}, {"field": "kw-classification", "value": "law-government-and-politics"}, {"field": "kw-concept", "value": ["formannskapet", "aktivitetsplikt", "innf\u00f8re aktivitetsplikt", "p\u00e5legger r\u00e5dmannen", "sak", "bystyret", "r\u00e5dmannen"]}, {"field": "kw-entity", "value": ["h\u00f8yres ingrid skj\u00f8tskift", "h\u00f8yre", "h\u00f8yres rolf jarle br\u00f8ske", "adresseavisen", "arbeiderpartiet", "frp"]}, {"field": "kw-location", "value": "trondheim"}, {"field": "kw-pageclass", "value": "article"}, {"field": "kw-taxonomy", "value": ["nyheter", "nyheter/trondheim"]}, {"field": "og-im